### Collection de validation de l'API my_distance
### Compatible REST Client (VS Code) / IntelliJ HTTP Client.
### Lancer l'app au prealable : (cd my_distance && flask --app app run)

@base = http://127.0.0.1:5000

### 1. Point d'entree (attendu : 200, corps {} )
GET {{base}}/api

### 2. Historique des distances (attendu : 200, tableau)
GET {{base}}/api/distances

### 3. Calcul nominal 3-4-5 (attendu : 200, result_distance = 5.0)
POST {{base}}/api/distance
Content-Type: application/json

{ "start_point": "0,0", "end_point": "3,4" }

### 4. Calcul exemple du sujet A(2,5) B(1,6) (attendu : 200, result_distance ~= 1.4142)
POST {{base}}/api/distance
Content-Type: application/json

{ "start_point": "2,5", "end_point": "1,6" }

### 5. PUT accepte (DEFAUT : se comporte comme POST)
PUT {{base}}/api/distance
Content-Type: application/json

{ "start_point": "0,0", "end_point": "3,4" }

### 6. GET sur /api/distance (DEFAUT : 415, lit request.json sans corps)
GET {{base}}/api/distance

### 7. Cle manquante (DEFAUT : 500 au lieu de 400)
POST {{base}}/api/distance
Content-Type: application/json

{ "start_point": "2,5" }

### 8. Coordonnee non numerique (DEFAUT : 500 au lieu de 400)
POST {{base}}/api/distance
Content-Type: application/json

{ "start_point": "a,b", "end_point": "1,6" }
